    <center><h2 style="color:white;">Our Mission</h2></center>
      <p class="about-text">Utah is well known for its fresh powdery snow, rugged mountains, 
      and an abundance of outdoor activities for all to enjoy.  However, it all comes at a price.
      For any resident who 
      has spent even one winter in this gorgeous valley environment, one thing we can all 
      agree on is that our air quality can be downright dismal during an inversion.  This is
      where Turn the Tide comes in.  Our project’s mission is to “turn the tide” against increasing
      pollution as Utah’s population grows.  It is an Android tracking application and 
      website interface committed towards increasing commuter awareness of the many alternatives 
      to driving a car in the Wasatch Front. With our project, we want Utahns to realize that
      it is simple and easy to take steps towards reducing pollution without sacrificing any of the 
      great lifestyle that comes with living in such a beautiful location.</p>
    <h4 style="color:white;">The Animal Points System</h4>
    <p class="about-text">The animal leveling and points system is based on animals that live within
    the Rocky Mountains of the United States.  By incorporating these animals, we hope users of our application
    are more committed towards helping our local environment by reducing their pollution.  As you level up, 
    you will encounter some of the most unique and beautiful animals who call our region home.</p>
